<h1 id="ingredients">Ingredients</h1>
<p>8 hard-boiled eggs
2 thick slices of boiled Ham
4 tomatoes
1 leek
1 piece of cucumber
2 tablespoon mayonnaise
1 tablespoon mustard
1 tablespoon White wine vinegar
Salt pepper
1 tablespoon Capers
1 bunch of chives
1 lettuce
1 bunch of dill or 1 packet of cress</p>

